				<div class="content">Simon, yes you can program now through the micro USB. It's not just a charging port, it's a serial communication and programming port. The only thing you can't do via USB is program the bootloader but Justine's already done that for you. The bootloader gives you the option to program via USB.<br>
<br>
HTH</div>
